@NODE DISKS "Disks"

     Disk -         A smaller disk icon for use on non-laced
                    displays.

     Kick -         As above, but a kick icon.  Use an icon
                    editor that can handle kick icons, or
                    Icon Update to copy to def_kick.

     HD -           A HD icon for non-laced displays, correct
