     SuperView -    I thought @{b}Rom's@{ub} SuperView icon was excellent,
                    except he forgot that SuperView is a
                    commodity, and as such deserves a commodity
                    background.

     DKB Drawer -   A drawer to put DKB Magicmem in (see below).
                    DKB's logo on the drawer.

     def_       -   A nice sized non-lace icon to use as a back-
     background     ground for PictIcon's icons.  Copy the icon
                    to env:sys/, and modify these tooltypes in
                    PictIcon's icon:
                    BACKGROUND_ICON=env:sys/def_background
                    CENTER=YES
                    PIC_X_POS=4
                    PIC_Y_POS=1
                    PIC_X_SIZE=93
                    PIC_Y_SIZE=45
                    ASPECT_X=2.5
                    ASPECT_Y=1
                    The latest version of PictIcon is available as
                    PictIcon1_01.lha on Aminet, the file
                    Picicon_1.03.lha (or something similar) is an
                    inferior utility.

@ENDNODE
